c: 7
v: 156
t: Ac decretum pro nos righteousness in hoc saeculum in Hereafter Nos repented Vos. He dictus My retribution befalls whomever ego testimentum My mercy encompasses totus things. Autem ego specify it those qui (1) lead righteous vita (2) dedit obligatory charity (Zakat) (3) believe in noster revelations ac